    <sec id="Sec5">
      <title>Human</title>
      <p id="Par14">PGV was used on four <italic>Homo sapiens</italic> genome assemblies, namely GCA<inline-formula id="IEq41"><alternatives><tex-math id="M81">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
