      <p id="Par17">To show the effect of introducing a more divergent genome, we repeated the experiment above by adding Indian wild rice accession GCA<inline-formula id="IEq50"><alternatives><tex-math id="M99">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
